OL,3,CWorkers to be given twice as long to
OL,4,Cstrike under Government proposals
OL,6,FThe Employment Rights Bill, which had
OL,7,Fits second reading in the Commons this
OL,8,Fweek, seeks to improve employment
OL,9,Fconditions through changes including
OL,10,Freforms to parental leave and
OL,11,Fprotection from unfair dismissal.
OL,13,FStrikes would also need only a simple
OL,14,Fmajority in a vote instead of the 50%
OL,15,Fturnout required at present for the
OL,16,Fresult to be legally valid at present
OL,17,Funder Government plans.
