OL,3,CWorkers to be given twice as long to
OL,4,Cstrike under Government proposals
OL,6,F"Our existing framework for industrial
OL,7,Frelations and collective bargaining is
OL,8,Ffull of inefficiencies and
OL,9,Fanachronisms that work against
OL,10,Fcooperation, compromise and
OL,11,Fcollaboration," they said.
OL,13,F"We want to create a positive and
OL,14,Fmodern framework for trade union
OL,15,Flegislation that delivers productive
OL,16,Fand constructive engagement, respects
OL,17,Fthe democratic mandate of unions, and
OL,18,Fworks to reset our industrial
OL,19,Frelations."
